    "No dev board in standard form factor — requires custom PCB",
    "Limited RGB LED support due to low RAM"
  ],
  "designNotes": [
    "Crystal-less USB is the killer feature — reduces BOM and PCB complexity",
    "Built-in DFU bootloader means end users can flash via USB without special tools",
